@startuml UC_19_Manage_Drafts
title UC-19: Manage Drafts

|User|
start
:(1) Open Drafts;

|System|
:(2) Load the user's draft list;
:(3) Return drafts to the UI;

|User|
:(4) Create or edit a draft;
:(5) Save the draft;

|System|
:(6) Validate ownership and draft content;
:(7) Store the draft changes;
if (Publish draft?) then (Yes)
  :(8) Create the post from the draft;
  :(9) Delete the draft after publishing;
else (No)
  :(10) Keep the draft for later editing;
endif
:(11) Return the updated draft state;

stop
@enduml
